{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"88e5208983","title":"毛泽东对叶群检讨信的几条批注","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7130b71420","index":0,"year":1970,"month":10,"day":15,"articleId":"88e5208983"}],"tags":[{"id":"62ff3f0cef","name":"叶群","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"232465f1a3","type":"title","text":"对叶群检讨信的几条批注","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88e5208983"},{"id":"95ec0fa232","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88e5208983"},{"id":"d28bada29f","type":"paragraph","text":"思想上政治上的路线正确与否是决定一切的。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88e5208983"},{"id":"1e700fe3ce","type":"paragraph","text":"爱吹不爱批，爱听小道消息，经不起风浪。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88e5208983"},{"id":"40ee83df5e","type":"paragraph","text":"一个倾向掩盖着另一个倾向。九大胜利，当上了中央委员，不得了了，要上天了，把九大路线抛到九霄云外，反九大的陈伯达路线在一些同志中占了上风了。请同志们研究一下，是不是这样的呢？","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88e5208983"},{"id":"83da41584f","type":"paragraph","text":"多年来不赞成读马、列的同志们，为何这时又向马、列求救，题目又是所谓论天才。不是在九大论过了吗，为何健忘若此？","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88e5208983"},{"id":"f71c1b107c","type":"paragraph","text":"不提九大，不提党章。也不听我的话。陈伯达一吹，就上劲了。军委办事组好些同志都是如此。党的政策是惩前毖后，治病救人，除了陈伯达待审查外，凡上当者都适用。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88e5208983"}],"page":{"id":"53d1dac22d","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"88e5208983","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}